divs: Sighting DetailsTraveling on U.S.1 South bound Jensen beach area,notice 3 disc shaped objects in horizontal formation,objects appeared to be very large considering the distance 10-15 miles away.These were not like looking at dots in the sky,they were of significant size and seemed to be over the ocean,my position for the viewing was approx.4.5 miles inland.The ST.Lucie nuclear plan is not far from this point to the north 6 miles approx ,4-5 years ago myself ,my mother and husband witnessed 3 stationary round objects in the same general area that sat in one spot for 9-10 mins before rapidly moving across the from east to west in the blink of an eye.Just an awsome expiriance on both occasions
